description: VT-12 in Worcester is now open, Single Lane closures throughout the week as work continues. Motorists are advised of gravel surfaces throughout the work area. Delays to be expected.
High water on VT-100 in Waterbury between Guptil Rd and Laurel Ln. Signs are in place. Drive with care.

VT-14 near Hope Cemetery down to Barre City is CLOSED to all traffic due to flooding in Barre City. (NO ACCESS TO BARRE CITY AT THIS TIME) Seek an alternate route.
Drive with caution on VT-14 between Barre City and Williamstown as there are multiple areas with water over the roadway. Seek an alternate route if possible.
